{
  "stem": "12506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Gliwice or Katowice, one of the two.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was big, because we walked there for about hours till we came to the other end of the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we slowed down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only they wouldn't let the people out of the house, I don't think there were no people in those houses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were trying to isolate one street there and get-- I mean, that was only-- when we got there already, there hundreds of camps from the area-- thousands and thousands of people, just like-- like cattle.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When you drive cattle through the town, that's exactly the way, today, I look back at it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pushing one another--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went-- at night we went through that city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever it was, no-- no sound of everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Snow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was cold, very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was snow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was ice on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember we had those Dutch wooden shoes, whatever you call it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We filled it out with paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We tied it to our foot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was good, because those shoes kept some warm in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we put straw in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We put cement paper-- we worked by the building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We filled it out with whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We put paper around our-- paper keeps your feet-- your body warm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everywhere.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Even around my back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we put paper all over our bodies to keep it-- keep it warm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No food and water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got something when we left the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I-- we didn't stop till we passed that city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did give us something for the, you know, for the way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know where we're going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know what's doing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't get food till we get out of that city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
